          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " For the reaction  197Au(g,n)196Au  activation yield",
                "  (formulae (4) of the article)",
                "           Y-act = N-act(196Au)/N-target(197Au)",
                "  was  measured  where  N-act is N-target multiplied",
                "  reaction integrated  cross section  (formulae (1))",
                "  and therefore Y-act is determined  as the reaction",
                "  integrated cross section in units B*MEV normalized",
                "  to N-target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainties presented in Fig.  8 are",
                " mainly from the determination of photon fluence. The",
                " statistical  uncertainties are very small and in the",
                " order of about 0.5 - 2.0  %."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The  systematic  uncertainties arise from the",
                " extrapolation of measured photopeak efficiencies  to",
                " the higher energies in 11B transitions (5 %)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic uncertainties arise  from  the",
